1.安装libevent
====================
  (1).下载libevent
      登录github，下载Libevent-release-2.0.22-stable
  (2).libevent安装环境准备
      $ sudo apt-get install automake
      $ sudo apt-get install libtool-bin
  (3).安装libevent
      $ unzip Libevent-release-2.0.22-stable
      $ cd Libevent-release-2.0.22-stable
      $ ./autogen.sh
      $ ./configure
      $ make
      $ make verify   #(optional)
      $ sudo make install
2.编译lightserver
====================
  $ make
